com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class GradeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.GradeType

  • public final class GradeType
extends Object
    One dimension of the grading notation used in the Schema.

    For example, for a grading system that classifies data using three grading classifications (1/2/3/4/5, A/B/C/D/E, and 1/2/3/4/5), there would be three GradeTypes. The first would have values from 1 to 5; the second would have values from A to E; and the third would also have values from 1 to 5.

    Since:
    1.0
